00:01:23,059 --> 00:01:30,515
[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]

2
00:01:31,991 --> 00:01:36,180
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:36,180 --> 00:01:37,820
Now, I pledge my loyalty to the nation,

4
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:39,776
willing to sacrifice my life.

5
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:44,340
If anyone dares to defame me in the future,

6
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,560
bringing unjust accusations upon my Father,

7
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,780
I promise that the Su family will face

8
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,340
dire consequences in Chang'an.

9
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,780
Your entire bloodline will be eradicated.

10
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,540
What absurdity are you spouting?

11
00:02:06,340 --> 00:02:07,700
If you don't believe it,

12
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:15,180
go ahead and try me!

13
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:25,320
As Minister possesses such ambition,

14
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,660
I am prepared to lead three hundred
skilled soldiers

15
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:30,660
to bolster Minister.

16
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,020
Remember,

17
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:47,780
they are colluding with the commander
of Khan Xingxiwang.

18
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,060
If they join forces,

19
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,400
how should we handle this?

20
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,500
If that's the case,

21
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,144
so what?

22
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:57,320
his time, we bring troops to Xizhou

23
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,780
to expose the collusion

24
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:01,740
between the Qu family and the rebels.

25
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:03,900
If this plan comes to fruition,

26
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:07,460
Chief Administrator
will have sufficient grounds

27
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:09,940
to take many lives.

28
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:12,660
However, we only have limited manpower.

29
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:15,500
If he brings those five thousand
northern cavalry…

30
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:16,500
Don't panic.

31
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:19,460
Xizhou is easy to defend
but difficult to conquer.

32
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,380
As long as we have hundreds of
skilled soldiers guarding it,

33
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:22,780
we can ensure the city's safety.

34
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,700
Additionally,

35
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:26,540
we still have Governor Qu under our control.

36
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,780
I bet those Xizhou garrison soldiers

37
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:30,460
wouldn't dare to resist easily.

38
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,700
I will embark on this journey
with three hundred skilled soldiers

39
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:36,680
merely to prevent them
from smuggling treasures in secret

40
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,980
to bribe the Northern soldiers to retreat

41
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:40,020
or to

42
