If he fails to break the siege this time,

45
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:52,380
he will find himself in a fatal situation.

46
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:54,660
If he does break the siege,

47
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:58,000
how many of the villagers he leads

48
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,100
will be left to return?

49
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,340
It is up to us

50
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:04,540
how to deal with him then.

51
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:08,460
Master, all we need to do today

52
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:11,240
is destroy all the token seals

53
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,500
found in the Governor's Mansion,

54
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:16,020
leaving them no chance
to report to the Emperor.

55
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,152
That's all.

56
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:20,820
Have you worked it out yet?

57
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,620
Do you wish to accompany me in solving

58
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:26,780
the siege of Tingzhou or not?

59
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:33,140
With Minister Qu's willingness
to issue a military order,

60
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:35,180
I will naturally place my trust in you.

61
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:36,224
Wait a minute.

62
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:39,020
How can you leave me out of the equation?

63
00:04:40,768 --> 00:04:41,856
I have a plan.

64
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:43,820
It may allow us to resolve the predicament

65
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:46,140
in Tingzhou without shedding blood.

66
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,860
Su Nanjin

67
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,460
