68
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,520
Last night, he tirelessly searched

69
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,880
the Governor's Mansion

70
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:25,520
and discovered various tokens and seals.
He promptly destroyed them,

71
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,540
severing our communication channels
with the imperial court.

72
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:31,340
We will set off early tomorrow.

73
00:05:31,872 --> 00:05:32,980
Within a day's time, you and Chongyu

74
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:35,900
must organize a hundred large carts
and gather five hundred warriors.

75
