The time is really a bit hurried.

76
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:40,900
I have gotten Xiao Tan to prepare food,

77
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,120
giving it to Cheng to carry.

78
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,140
You are not allowed to be hungry.

79
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,140
Do you hear me?

80
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:45,216
Don't worry.

81
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,340
I will surely return unscathed.

82
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:50,340
Today, I shall visit the Great Buddha Temple

83
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,620
to recite scriptures and pray for you.

84
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,940
I will bring back a protective charm.

85
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,900
If I happen to return late,
you may go to sleep without waiting up for me.

86
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,820
You never believe in these things.

87
