Do not worry.

133
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:56,540
I know people in all 10 tribes in the North,

134
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:59,180
so it should be a safe trip to Tingzhou.

135
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,620
Although it's sunny today,

136
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:02,740
it's still a bit cold.

137
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:05,220
Have a bowl of ginger soup after you go back.

138
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:06,912
And don't forget to take your medicine.

139
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,980
You can't catch a cold again this year.

140
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:11,552
Okay.

141
00:10:13,568 --> 00:10:14,624
Liuli,

142
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:17,980
I can't be with you for the new year this year,

143
00:10:18,944 --> 00:10:20,064
but at the Lantern Festival,

144
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:22,060
I will certainly bring back good news.

145
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,224
I'll be waiting for you.

146
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:10,180
Senior Official Pei's carriage

147
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,740
just looked great,

148
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:14,940
so many broke down on the road
after just one day.

149
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:19,180
We had to camp out way earlier than planned.

150
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:21,500
At this rate,

151
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:23,100
it'll take us at least half a month

152
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:24,380
to reach Tingzhou.

153
