What is actually going on?

163
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:39,520
I still have matters to discuss with Shouyue.

164
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:41,100
Is there something
you can't say in front of him?

165
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:51,620
Madam, what's the matter?

166
00:12:52,780 --> 00:12:54,260
I have concealed something from Shouyue.

167
00:12:54,260 --> 00:12:56,220
That's why I asked Yunyi
to invite Minister over,

168
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,220
so we can have a word in private.

169
00:12:58,220 --> 00:12:59,880
Madam, what have you been keeping from Shouyue?

170
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,660
I would like to hear the details.

171
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:04,540
I wish to get a protective charm

172
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:05,740
for Shouyue and Minister.

173
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,360
but I can't get a protective charm

174
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,940
all by myself.

175
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,140
I need your help.

176
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,020
What's it about the protective charm,

177
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,100
and why does it have to be a secret
from Shouyue?

178
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:17,980
Shouyue is a great guy and all,

179
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:20,540
but he's just too strict about following rules.

180
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:23,340
Things are pretty pressing right now,

181
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:25,260
and sometimes
you've got to do what's necessary in a crunch.

182
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,980
For someone like Shouyue,

183
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,380
if he knew about this,

184
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:29,540
