185
00:13:29,540 --> 00:13:31,380
So, I had to act first and tell him later.

186
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,840
I decided to meet Minister privately

187
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,060
to get this protective charm first.

188
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,620
I want to ask

189
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:38,900
what exactly is this protective charm.

190
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:40,512
Token of passage.

191
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:43,104
Token of passage.

192
00:13:46,020 --> 00:13:47,680
