199
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:02,800
who are skilled in crafting delicate objects.

200
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,800
These people have to be not only skillful

201
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:07,420
but also undyingly loyal to you.

202
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:10,300
