208
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:27,980
Previously, I hid this from Shouyue

209
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:30,000
and secretly made a mode of token of passage.

210
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,140
I just did not expect

211
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:33,360
that I would need to use it

212
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,540
so soon.

213
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:38,220
Another thing being hidden from Shouyue.

214
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:40,256
However,

215
00:14:40,256 --> 00:14:41,280
Madam,

216
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:43,220
you've come through for us big time again.

217
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:53,380
So this is the protective charm
that you got for me

218
